.TH TRANCE-APPLET 1 "June 2026" "trance" "Trance Screensaver COSMIC Applet"
.SH NAME
trance-applet \- COSMIC panel applet for managing the trance screensaver daemon
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B trance-applet
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B trance-applet
is the System76 COSMIC Desktop panel applet for the trance screensaver. It runs as part of the cosmic-panel and displays status in the tray, allowing users to toggle screensaver states and launch settings.
.SH AUTHOR
Screensavers Developer <dev@local76.org>
